name: Pixel Ripped 1995
summary: It’s time to get on the most nostalgic gaming ride of your life! On this Virtual Reality nostalgia trip, you have to join forces with our hero Dot to save the gaming world as we know it from the clutches of the evil Cyblin Lord and become the hero of Far-of-a-Land! During your adventures, you’ll find unique characters, games, and gaming systems that will guide you throughout the good ol’ 90s!
